Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.43,0:01:34.09,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen,\ngood evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.00,0:01:37.80,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The life of the young boy that\nwas sacrificed to my friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.91,0:01:40.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...was cradled in the pure soul's arms\nas it faded away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.61,0:01:43.17,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And I rejoiced.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:46.14,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,His soul has at long last\nbeen tainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.78,0:01:51.65,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Tainted by the fires of a remorse and hatred\nwhich will never fade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.17,0:02:08.40,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Franz?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.24,0:02:13.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You promised me that you wouldn't go away\nanymore without telling me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.25,0:02:31.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz... I couldn't bring myself to go to\nyour funeral no matter how hard I tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.69,0:02:37.93,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How could I? Right up until yesterday,\nyou were by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:42.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You were always there for me\nwhen I needed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.94,0:02:47.17,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But now, all I have\nis this letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.78,0:02:53.27,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why did it have to be you?\NWhy was it you instead of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:59.41,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Franz, answer me...\NJust like you always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:04.98,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Say something...\NSay anything, Franz...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:08.62,count fo,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,350)}Act 19:\NEven if I Should Stop Being Me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.70,0:03:14.67,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Queen to F3.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:21.37,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Pawn, C7 to C6.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.75,0:03:30.88,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Danglars Bank stocks have posted\ntrading limit highs for several days now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:33.62,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Knight to E4.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:39.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Queen, B6 to C7.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.89,0:03:40.32,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Every stock in his investment portfolio\nis on an explosive growth trend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:43.62,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That Andrea kid did his job\na lot better than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.73,0:03:47.96,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. We will start flooding\nhis investments with sell-offs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.27,0:03:50.17,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Paris market goes without saying,\nbut the Eastern,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:52.03,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...Kingdom, and Frontier\nmarkets, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:56.20,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keep flooding all of them with sell-offs\nin succession until each market closes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:57.50,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.81,0:04:00.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Pawn to C4.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:03.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Excellency...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:05.29,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Knight, D5 to E7.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.42,0:04:05.29,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Haidee wishes to speak\nwith you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:10.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Count, I love you more\nthan I did my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:13.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot bear to see you\nchange any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:18.93,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, continuing to do this would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.66,0:04:18.93,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Knight, E4 to G5.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:20.86,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Unnecessary pawns are to be\nsacrificed without mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.14,0:04:22.94,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Knight to C8.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:24.20,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Everything that stands between me\nand my revenge! Without mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:26.86,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bertuccio!\NTake Haidee away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.31,0:04:28.97,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Very good, Excellency.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:34.04,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Count! Did you only save me so that you\ncould use me as a tool for revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:36.62,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You are not\nthat sort of man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:41.09,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Count, I have faith in you!\NCount!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:42.82,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Count!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.69,0:04:45.35,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Pawn to C5.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:48.75,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The game is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:54.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The end is almost\nupon us...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:58.93,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just take a look at today's\nstock prices, Andrea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:01.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wipe the smile\nfrom my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:03.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:06.80,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I owe my success to you.\NI'm in your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:08.21,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:12.35,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, about the\nwedding ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:15.98,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's being stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.09,0:05:21.43,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Something about a friend dying suddenly,\nso she can't get married anytime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:25.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I have no idea where that girl\ngets her stubborn streak from.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:26.96,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, it's\nquite understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:30.80,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, how is\nher mother doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:34.01,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's been bedridden for quite some time.\NPerhaps if I went and offered her my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:38.51,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! If you were to keep her company,\NI'm sure it would take her mind off things!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:42.01,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I certainly hope that\nyou are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:48.74,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How much longer will our bank's assets\ncontinue to multiply like this? Right, Michelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:50.12,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:52.29,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Open the display!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:56.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Every last one of my stocks\nis humming along smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:11.44,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:18.15,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert, listen to me.\NI'm thinking of leaving Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:21.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me\nto my home town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:26.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Admittedly, life there won't be as\nextravagant as we're used to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:31.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If it's just the two of us, I have enough\nsaved away to at least keep us fed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:34.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What about Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:38.03,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're a real opportunist,\naren't you, Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:39.63,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.74,0:06:41.61,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've had all I can take!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:45.51,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When you get right down to it, it's you and\nyour old friends' fault that this happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:50.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I got caught in the middle of you and\nyour old lovers' sick love triangle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:53.95,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who gives a damn about\NEdmond Dantes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:59.16,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why are my friends and l...\NWhy did Franz, of all people, have to die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:03.86,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert, where are\nyou going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:06.16,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.\NNowhere in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:08.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what\nhappens to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:12.26,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody would be better off\nif I had died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.74,0:07:20.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to blame me for what happened,\ngo ahead and blame me for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:28.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But you shouldn't... You shouldn't\nthink so little of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:50.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Permit, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.94,0:07:53.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have one. They always\nlet me pass through.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.48,0:07:58.35,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you really shouldn't go around\nthinking you're still an aristocrat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:04.21,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your ID number's already been revoked.\NYou can't come and go as you please anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:05.72,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:07.52,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.66,0:08:11.15,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Like they say, a stupid father is gonna\nhave nothing but stupid kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:13.76,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Go get yourself\na permit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.23,0:08:16.63,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's assuming that they'll\neven give you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:17.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:25.27,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:33.75,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You fraudulent\npiece of crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:41.93,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that! Get off my bike!\NGet your hands off it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:43.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:45.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're fighting ME,\nremember?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:51.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think that you can still\nboss us around! Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:09.51,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This state is most unbecoming a\nbeautiful lady such as yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:13.69,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.\NI'm always alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:15.46,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:19.63,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing you sad simply\ntears my heart in two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:24.37,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Men always say things like that\nto try to make me feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:30.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will always be by your side.\NMother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:34.44,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Andrea...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:42.41,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, just for today... Just for now...\NCall me Victoria.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:44.69,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Victoria, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:05.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:16.72,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Albert?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:21.39,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz?\NFranz, is that you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:24.16,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into you?\NAre you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:26.50,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:28.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:30.50,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:33.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad\nyou're all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:36.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is this any time for you to be\nworrying about someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:39.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:45.92,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert! Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:45.92,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert! Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:49.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations,\NMonsieur Albert.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.99,0:10:52.29,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations.\NWhat kept you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.59,0:10:55.65,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What have you been up to?\NShe's been waiting for you for ages!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:10:57.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:03.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Eugenie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:07.77,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert, congratulations\non turning sixteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:15.25,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're going at it\nin broad daylight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:17.51,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Save that stuff for when you're\nin private, will ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:21.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen, allow me\nto introduce the man...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:23.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...without whom this party\nwould not be complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:27.76,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The man who saved Albert's life on Luna,\nthe Count of Monte Cristo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:37.19,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz, we can't! We can't\ninvite this man to Paris!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:41.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? We both insisted\nthat he come visit, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.81,0:11:45.24,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look. Everybody says that they're\ndying to meet the Count.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:49.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can't! He's a demon who's come back\nto Paris to get revenge on us all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:54.02,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Darling, why don't you introduce yourself first?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.22,0:11:52.82,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Father! Mother! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:55.12,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Eugenie and Franz! You, too! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:55.12,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm feeling a little shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:57.92,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Get as far away from him\nas you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:02.72,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Count!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:05.46,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your kind invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:05.13,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:09.50,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Franz!\NHe's the man who killed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:11.16,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"My, how fascinating."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:15.61,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, I'm begging you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:41.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is for Franz!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.31,0:12:50.47,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Albert?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:56.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one\nwho killed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:13:01.38,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert, when you think about it,\nit was you who killed me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.29,0:13:04.59,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.06,0:13:04.92,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:06.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:09.73,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You only think of yourself,\nand you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.80,0:13:15.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I tried to tell you something,\nyou never listened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.34,0:13:17.39,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No! Franz, it wasn't\nlike that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:21.27,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hate you. I'll hate you\nfor as long as I live.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.54,0:13:27.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ow... It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.58,0:13:29.74,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:29.89,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.92,0:13:31.35,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.45,0:13:32.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:33.09,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:34.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz, I'm sorry!\NFranz!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:35.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:42.46,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, Franz!\NDon't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:44.12,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.43,0:13:46.76,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's something that\NI have to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:49.40,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So don't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.67,0:13:51.93,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No! Franz, don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.17,0:13:53.14,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:55.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,FRANZ!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:14:03.12,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Albert, are you okay?\NSnap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.45,0:14:05.18,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Albert!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.42,0:14:06.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:08.19,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:12.79,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's nothing to worry about\nif you can still move like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:14.16,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Renaud?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:18.43,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.53,0:14:21.76,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,By coincidence, I spotted\na guy riding your bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:26.73,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Relax, your bike is safe.\NThe evildoers have been punished!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:28.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.11,0:14:33.21,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about? Everybody needs\na tool-loving, bike-loving friend, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:37.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Admittedly, I pushed her so hard to get here\nthat she's in pretty bad shape now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:43.98,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea how badly\NI've been waiting for today to arrive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:47.35,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I looked everywhere for rare parts,\nendured setback after setback,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.46,0:14:49.39,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and finally got her\nin working order!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:53.36,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Chest swelled with anticipation, I set out in high\nspirits for a long drive, and what happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.47,0:14:56.46,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Hm? Why, that's Albert's bike!\NBut who's that on it?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.57,0:14:59.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So I pull up to him, planning to\nask him what's going on, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:01.04,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme that ratchet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:03.24,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:11.74,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My baby's showing signs\nof a recovery!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.19,0:15:13.15,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you being\noverly dramatic?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.25,0:15:17.52,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Overly dramatic," nothing! There's no sadder\nsight than a machine that can't be fixed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.76,0:15:21.45,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I had the same problem that night we\nrescued Valentine. That was so terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.76,0:15:23.19,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That was YOUR car?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.43,0:15:27.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It sure was... You have no idea how\nbad my heart was broken that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:30.59,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How can you talk like that?\NValentine was about to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:31.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get me wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.64,0:15:34.37,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I volunteered my car because they said\nthey were gonna go rescue Valentine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:40.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, I used to have\na thing for Valentine...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.95,0:15:42.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You never said\na word about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.82,0:15:47.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Albert... Do you remember\nwhen we came out here on a drive?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.02,0:15:49.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:54.76,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a little while ago, but\nit feels like a distant memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.73,0:16:00.39,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That quiche that Valentine shared\nwith us was great, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:05.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:11.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I was just remembering\nthat day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:17.04,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz is a lucky guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.05,0:16:20.35,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're always\nthinking about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.76,0:16:26.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I only have machines to soothe\nmy troubled heart now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.66,0:16:30.63,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Renaud...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.47,0:16:35.03,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, let's head back\nand grab something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.24,0:16:39.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:48.25,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Michelle!\NWe're being swamped with sell-offs!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:49.47,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:52.14,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am trying as best I can to prop up the prices,\nbut I am unable to keep up with the volume.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:54.52,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sink all the money we have\ninto it to stop the slide!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:59.09,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't just our bank stocks or those of\nour business group that are crashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:03.52,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Every stock that we have invested in\nis in a nosedive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:06.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:08.20,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am unable to determine\nthe cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:11.04,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Unable to determine\nthe cause"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:16.11,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Pull it together, damn it!\NIf this keeps up, I'll go bankrupt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:21.11,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Infection by unknown\nvirus detec... ted...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.61,0:17:21.93,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:23.68,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...ted...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.32,0:17:25.32,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Eastern market\nis open now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.58,0:17:26.35,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...ted...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:28.62,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Pull out our shares! Sell off everything\nbut our bank stocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.05,0:17:30.28,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...ted...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.70,0:17:30.32,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Convert it to cash!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.66,0:17:33.29,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Today's weather in Paris\nis sunny... sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:37.75,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Current temperature is 22 Celsi... sunny... with\nless than a 10% chance of precipita... sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:36.20,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:41.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It is shaping up to be\na pleasant day... sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:40.47,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Michelle! Snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:41.73,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:43.67,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sunny, sunny, sunny, sunny...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.77,0:17:43.24,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Eastern market...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:48.94,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Paris market closed today with prices\nconsiderably lower than yesterday's... sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.61,0:17:48.94,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle, start running these\nnumbers immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:53.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The prevailing opinion is that the market\nturned against overextended businesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:52.65,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't keep up with it by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:53.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The prevailing opinion is that the market\nturned against overextended businesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:55.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...as a result of the sudden sell-off\nof Danglars Group stocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.48,0:17:55.91,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.02,0:17:59.62,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sunny, sunny, sunny,\nsunny, sunny...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:17:59.62,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:02.38,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At the outbreak of this market run...\nsunny, sunny, sunny...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:04.98,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the influx of capital from\nouter space sources was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:04.98,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.83,0:18:14.60,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Father? What's the matter?\NWhy are you barging in like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:26.04,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Eugenie, dear daughter of mine...\NI have something to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:27.93,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Something to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:29.55,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Something wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.35,0:18:35.69,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, your wedding with Andrea\nhas been set for the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:41.69,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do that?! I told that you I can't\nget married so soon after Franz died!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:42.95,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:43.76,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.86,0:18:45.49,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.90,0:18:48.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that you don't care\nif l... no, this entire family...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.20,0:18:52.19,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...dies penniless in a ditch somewhere\nthanks to your self-centeredness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:54.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Father, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:57.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down?!\NHow am I supposed to calm down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:19:01.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My stocks have taken a nosedive! They aren't\nworth the paper they're printed on now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.48,0:19:04.94,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Give up on this worthless\npiano nonsense of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:07.95,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're not serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.42,0:19:11.08,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one\nwho can save this family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.49,0:19:14.86,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to marry Andrea\nright away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.36,0:19:17.59,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But what about\nmy feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:19.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They don't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.23,0:19:22.67,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All that matters to me\nis that I get my money back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.61,0:19:30.51,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to this, Andrea's fortune\nwill be mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:37.04,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Eugenie, at this moment, you're the\nmost precious thing in the world to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:55.09,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz is still here\nwith us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.30,0:19:57.96,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's the way\NI see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:20:02.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I get the feeling that he's showing us\nwhat path we have to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.92,0:20:16.22,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Renaud...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.60,0:20:35.06,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And where might you be going\nat this late hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:49.49,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.86,0:20:51.08,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:53.59,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.37,0:21:00.96,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.04,0:21:04.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even the daughter\nof an aristocrat...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.00,0:21:08.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...would be ruined for life if something\nlike this is done to her, wouldn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.47,0:21:09.74,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.55,0:21:15.61,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The day after tomorrow,\nyou're going to belong to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.58,0:21:20.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The main course will\nhave to wait until then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.62,0:21:27.18,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert, save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.36,0:21:30.62,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.13,0:23:12.72,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up\non your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.17,0:23:16.40,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No matter the time, no matter the place,\nyou're never alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.17,0:23:19.73,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Gankutsuou,\NThe Count of Monte Cristo, act 20...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.62,0:23:21.17,count fo,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,352)}Act 20:\NFarewell, Eugenie
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.84,0:23:21.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,..."Farewell, Eugenie."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:23.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bide your time,\nand hold out hope!
